ivardefs.name: firstDose
ivardefs.desc: The first dose (dose quantity) administered in humans can be specified, for a product under investigation, using a numerical value and its unit of measurement.

ivardefs.name: maxDosePerDay
ivardefs.desc: The maximum dose per day (maximum dose quantity to be administered in any one 24-h period) that can be administered as per the protocol referenced in the clinical trial authorisation.

ivardefs.name: maxDosePerTreatmentPeriod
ivardefs.desc: The maximum dose per treatment period that can be administered as per the protocol referenced in the clinical trial authorisation.

ivardefs.name: maxSingleDose
ivardefs.desc: The maximum single dose that can be administered as per the protocol of a clinical trial can be specified using a numerical value and its unit of measurement.

ivardefs.name: maxTreatmentPeriod
ivardefs.desc: The maximum treatment period during which an Investigational Medicinal Product can be administered as per the protocol referenced in the clinical trial authorisation.

ivardefs.name: targetSpecies_
ivardefs.desc: A species for which this route applies.

properties.desc: The path by which the pharmaceutical product is taken into or makes contact with the body.
